TOU
# tou2d runtime asset dir — user copies SHP/WAV/OGG from their TOU
# install into here (see examples/tou2d/TOU_PLAN.md § M4.8). The
# original game's assets are NOT redistributable; not tracked in git.
# `assets/*` (not `assets`) so per-subdir re-inclusion works for
# the permissively-licensed M6.0 UI font (see exception below).
assets/*
# M6.0 — exception: the bundled UI font is permissively licensed
# (DejaVu Sans Mono, Bitstream-Vera-derivative). Ships in-tree so a
# fresh checkout has a default usable font without manual install.
# Drop-in replaceable (see assets/ui/README.md).
!assets/ui/
